# Heavy / non-web artifacts — Vercel builds `dist` remotely from source,
# so none of these should be uploaded. Keeps the deploy bundle small and
# under the 100 MB single-file limit (dist-electron holds the installer exe).
node_modules
.git
dist
dist-electron
android
electron
playwright-report
test-results
docs
.claude
.github
supabase
scripts
*.log
*.apk
*.exe
*.aab
